UID:eb2P_DDPmVl3Ouz3rMPx8
SUMMARY:Trail Explorers - Kelly's Brook Trail
DTSTAMP:20260317T215404Z
DTSTART:20260318T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join the Trail Explorers on Wednesday\, March 18\, at 10:30 a.m
	. They will be exploring Kelly's Brook Trail\, and the meeting location is
	 the Farmer’s Market: 245 Freshwater Road. Upper parking lot. This trail i
	s 4 km and will take approximately 60-75 minutes to complete. It is rated 
	a 3 on the difficulty scale \\(on a 1-5 scale\, with 1 being the easiest a
	nd 5 being the hardest. For more information please visit: https://www.stj
	ohns.ca/en/recreation-culture/trail-explorers.aspx This initiative provide
	s a wonderful opportunity to explore the beautiful trails throughout the c
	ity\, promoting health\, wellness\, and community connection. Please conta
	ct healthyprograms@stjohns.ca for further information.\n\nhttps://seatoday
	.6amcity.com/events/#/details/trail-explorers-kelly-s-brook-trail/18083541
	/2026-03-18T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/trail-explorers-kelly-s-b
	rook-trail/18083541/2026-03-18T00
LOCATION:Farmer's Market: 245 Freshwater Road. Upper parking lot\, 4749 Bal
	lard Ave NW\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-sports
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
